			"elements": [
				{
					"type": "html",
					"name": "question1",
					"html": "<p>Prior to submitting a request, ensure alternatives such as purchasing or delivery of items have been considered and deemed not viable.</p>\n\n<p>If this request relates to a Duty to Accommodate Plan, managers should contact their Labour Relations Advisor for advice and guidance. In the event the employee requires support to retrieve a larger asset related to a DTA (i.e. chair), there is a pick-up and delivery service available through the <a href=\"http://jusnet.justice.gc.ca/eng/work-travail/facil-install/juspace.html\" target=\"_blank\">National Accommodations Division</a> available through the JUSpace link on the JUSnet home page.</p>"
				}
			],
